  "title": "Spicy Crumbly Argentinian Ancho Peppers Crockpot Crumble",
  "description": "A smoky, crumbly dish featuring dried red chillies that is perfect for those sick days. Halal-friendly and ideal as a snack or side dish.",
  "cuisine": "Argentinean",
